Package: alto
Type: Package
Title: Aligns Topics across LDA Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kris", "Sankaran", email = "ksankaran@wisc.edu",role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Laura","Symul", email = "lsymul@stanford.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Julia", "Fukuyama", email = "jfukuyam@iu.edu", role = c("aut"))
    )
Maintainer: Laura Symul <lsymul@stanford.edu>
Description: "alto" is an R package that aligns topics from different LDA models,
    computes metrics for quantifying the goodness of alignment,
    and provides visualization functions to explore the alignment and robustness of topics across environments or LDA hyper-parameters.
